snippet.title: Atom Idle Incremental Game
snippet.description:
Atom Idle Incremental Game
Atom Merge is an interesting idle game where you can collect all the known elements from Hydrogen to Oganesson.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AG.atomMerge
